title: 19 Kids And Counting S08E02E03 WS DSR x264-[NY2] mp4
description:
Season 08, Episode 02 - Double Dating Duggars
 When Jim Bob & Michelle take new couple, Jessa & Ben, out on a double date, they discuss the importance of boundaries. Anna builds a playhouse. Jill and her buddy group make the Duggars' favorite snack. And the family may be in for more changes...

Season 08, Episode 03 - Another Courtship?
 Another courtship may be on the horizon! The kids plan a surprise for their parents. In DC, Anna has her hands full taking care of the two boys, and Mackynzie. Jim Bob and Michelle make a decision that could change one of their daughters' lives.
